Hotkey:
  0: usage guide
  `: overall workflow
  1: base, image selection, & noise injection
  2: embedding, fine tune string, auto prompts, & adv conditioning parameters
  3: lora, controlnet parameters, & adv model parameters
  4: refine parameters
  5: detailer parameters
  6: upscale parameters

Workflow Control:
  All switches in any Workflow panel take effect in realtime.
  All switches in any Select panel also affect sub workflow, but don't take effect in realtime. Some switches in Parameters panel that affect sub workflow don't take effect in realtime also.
  Switches in Workflow panels include all workflow switch functions in Select and Parameters panels.
  Suggested method:
  Preprocessing Queue Prompt needs to be executed once before actural generation if use switches in Select or Parameters panels only to control the sub workflow, the state of correspoding switches in Workflow panels will be changed automatically after the preprocess. So that it's recommended to disable all process in Overall Workflow panel and adjust all parameters and sub-workflow-related switches before actural genaration.
  Alternative method:
  Use switches in Overall and Sub Workflow panels to control the workflow which takes effects in realtime, but remember to adjust the corresponding switches in Select and Parameters panel to the same state as in Sub Workflow panels before the Queue Prompt.

Workflow-panel-only switches (realtime):
  Progress switches (in Overall Workflow JK🐉)
  SD15 ELLA Text Encode (in Base Model Sub Workflow JK🐉)
  SDXL Text Ecode (in Base Model Sub Workflow JK🐉)
  Self-Attention Guidance (in Base Adv Model Sub Workflow JK🐉)
  LCM Model Sampling Discrete (in Base Adv Model Sub Workflow JK🐉)
  FreeU_V2 (in Base Adv Model Sub Workflow JK🐉)
  Rescale CFG (in Base Adv Model Sub Workflow JK🐉)
  Base IP Adapter (in Base Adv Model Sub Workflow JK🐉)
  SDXL Refine Text Encode (in Refine Sub Workflow JK🐉)
  Refine 1 + 2 (in Refine Sub Workflow JK🐉)
  IPAdapter 2 - FaceID (in Refine Sub Workflow JK🐉)
  Face Detailer (in Detailer Sub Workflow JK🐉)
  Hand Detailer (in Detailer Sub Workflow JK🐉)
  Image Upscale ControlNet Tile (in Upscale Sub Workflow JK🐉)

Parameter-panel-only switches (needs preprocessing):
  swap_dimensions (in Base Model Parameters JK🐉)
  save_ckpt_hash (in Base Model Parameters JK🐉)
  Enable_refine_1_seed (in Refine Model Parameters JK🐉)
  Enable_refine_1_prompt (in Refine Model Parameters JK🐉)
  Enable_refine_2_seed (in Refine Model Parameters JK🐉)
  Enable_refine_2_prompt (in Refine Model Parameters JK🐉)
  save_ckpt_hash (in Refine Model Parameters JK🐉)
  Enable_upscale_prompt (in Upscale Model Parameters JK🐉)
  save_ckpt_hash (in Upscale Model Parameters JK🐉)

Metadata:
  All parameters including sub-workflow-related switches will affect the generation result and also the content of Metadata saved with the image.
  It's recommended to keep the value of ckpt or vae loaders in the Parameters panel the same selection as Primitive Loaders above.
  In Refine image saving, remove noise_jinection_metadata link if not refining any noise injection process.
  In Upscale image saving, remove noise_jinection_metadata or refine_metadata link if not using Noise Injection or refine process.
  In Detailer image saving, remove noise_jinection_metadata, refine_metadata or upscale_metadata link if not using Noise Injection or refine process.

SDXL:
  Load SDXL Ckpt for Base | Refine (Optional) | Upscale
  Load SDXL Vae
  Disable SD15 ELLA Text Encode (in Base Model Sub Workflow JK🐉)
  Enable SDXL Text Ecode (in Base Model Sub Workflow JK🐉)     (Optional)
  Enable SDXL Refine Text Encode (in Refine Sub Workflow JK🐉) (optional)
  Disable IPAdapter 2 - faceid (in Refine Sub Workflow JK🐉)
  Switch plus and plus-face ipadapter to sdxl_vit-h version
  Disable Image Upscale ControlNet Tile (in Upscale Sub Workflow JK🐉)

Other:
  1. Nodes State JK🐉 uses target nodes' id to control their active | mute | bypass mode. Need to update node_id_list if you make a copy.
  2. The order of Detailer Progress and Upscale Progress can be swapped. Avoid to form loops.
Change ControlNet Tile Model for sd15 | sdxl.
